    <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
      VITA-SOH provides a compliance-grade software measurement instrument for
      battery State-of-Health (SOH) and Digital Product Passport (DPP) generation.
      Our system is designed for reproducibility, auditability, and regulatory trust —
      not black-box automation.
    </p>

    <h2>What We Do</h2>
    <p>
      We help battery OEMs, recyclers, and operators generate EU-ready battery passport
      data using a deterministic AI measurement engine combined with explicit
      interpretation and compliance rules.
    </p>

    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <p>
      Battery telemetry and test data are processed by a frozen, offline AI model.
      Outputs are interpreted through rule-based logic, logged for audit traceability,
      and mapped directly to EU Battery Passport fields.
    </p>

    <h2>Pilot Program</h2>
    <p>
      We are currently running pilot programs with selected partners to validate
      SOH interpretation, passport data generation, and audit procedures using
      real production data.
    </p>

